Beáta es, * María, quæ credidísti: perficiéntur in te, quæ dicta sunt tibi a Dómino, <text:span text:style-name="Rubric">(</text:span>allelúja<text:span text:style-name="Rubric">)</text:span>.
Blessed art thou, * O Mary, who didst believe: those things shall be fulfilled in thee which were spoken to thee by the Lord, <text:span text:style-name="Rubric">(</text:span>alleluia<text:span text:style-name="Rubric">)</text:span>.
